<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>教学 on Bore's Notes</title><link>https://bore.vip/shuoshuotags/%E6%95%99%E5%AD%A6/</link><description>Recent content in 教学 on Bore's Notes</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 14:12:43 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://bore.vip/shuoshuotags/%E6%95%99%E5%AD%A6/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>圆柱切拼成长方体</title><link>https://bore.vip/shuoshuo/j4y10lwm/</link><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 14:08:56 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://bore.vip/shuoshuo/j4y10lwm/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;圆柱切拼成近似长方体。拼成的长方体的长等于圆柱底面周长的一半，宽等于圆柱的底面半径，高等于圆柱的高。它的体积不变，增加的表面积是长方体左右两个面面积之和。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>